    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is always so rushed and i dont really want to deal with the whole formal appointment thing just to ask about a supplement. i read that st johns wort works on the same serotonin pathways so if i just wait a few days for the zoloft to clear my system, isn't it basically just a safer version of the same thing? like, is there actually a huge risk if i just transition myself over a weekend?",
